      "name": "Consume Flesh",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The cinder ghoul is adjacent to the corpse of a creature that died within the last hour.</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The cinder ghoul devours a chunk of the corpse and regains [[/r 5d6]] Hit Points. It can regain Hit Points from any given corpse only once.</p>"
